snippet: George W. Bush has stayed out of the spotlight since leaving the White House, but he recently welcomed his first grandchild and, next week, he will dedicate his expansive presidential center.
abstract: George W and Laura Bush welcome arrival of their first grandchild, born to daughter Jenna and her husband Henry Hager, one week before opening of Bush's 226,565-square-foot presidential library in Dallas.
lead_paragraph: George W. Bush has stayed out of the spotlight since leaving the White House, but he recently welcomed his first grandchild and, next week, he will dedicate his expansive presidential center.
